---
import styles from "./AboutMe.module.css";
---

<section class={styles.aboutMe}>
    <div class="container">
        <div class={styles.content}>
            <div class={styles.left}>
                <p>
                    <strong>Victor Adebowale Momodu</strong> is a software engineer
                    focused on building fast, thoughtful, and scalable digital products.
                </p>

                <p>
                    With a strong foundation in modern software development,
                    Victor works across frontend and backend systems, using
                    tools and languages like Astro, JavaScript, TypeScript,
                    Python, and Golang to create reliable and maintainable
                    solutions.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class={styles.right}>
                <p>
                    Working across the intersection of design and engineering,
                    Victor brings precision, curiosity, and strong technical
                    thinking to every project.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Clean code, thoughtful systems, and products built with
                    intention.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
